title: Toxic Relationships
description:
In this episode, Jessi and Stew are joined by Addie Mackay, another stylist and educator at JZ Styles Co. They talk about dealing with toxic relationships; both professional and personal. See what advice they have to give on dealing with hard situations as they share some of their personal experiences!
